These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-8-1::.
House: futuristic, wooden
There 2 different types of food: radish, cauliflower
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike
1. the person eating radish is not to the left of the person driving the helicopter##8
2. the futuristic house is on the right of the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| House         | wooden   | futuristic |
| Food   | radish | cauliflower    |
| Transport     | helicopter  | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, water
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, vegafina
There 2 different types of food: pear, spinach
1. the person drinking mirinda is in an even position##4
2. the person eating pear is not to the right of the havana-smoker##8
3. the havana-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person drinking mirinda##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Beverage      | water    | mirinda    |
| Cigar   | havana | vegafina    |
| Food     | pear  | spinach |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-8-3::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: taxi, trike
The people have 2 different jobs:  manager, project-manager
There are 2 different favourite colors: coral, brown
1. the person driving the taxi is not to the right of the person who likes brown##8
2. the project-manager is not the person who likes brown##6
3. the manager is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |        2        |
| Transport      | taxi   | trike           |
| Job           | manager | project-manager |
| Color   | brown  | coral      |

