1. the architect is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Birthday         | january | december    |
| Job           | architect  | dressmaker |
| Game   | mah-jongg      | backgammon    |

